<P>
LAGOS, September 16 (Xinhua) -- The West African peace-keeping
force ECOMOG has recaptured four villages in northern Sierra
Leone earlier this week, killing at least 10 rebels, a report
from Freetown said Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
