<HEADLINE> Ethiopia Says More Ethiopians Expelled From </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ADDIS ABABA, September 16 (Xinhua) -- The Office of Ethiopian
Government Spokeswoman Selome Taddesse said Wednesday that
Ethiopians are still suffering great hardship in Eritrea.
