Russia's main trading floor, showed an even steeper drop. The
ruble fell to 12.59 rubles to the dollar at the close of trade
Wednesday, down from Tuesday's high of 7.3 rubles.
(Russia-Ruble-Dive)
</P>
<P>
- - - -
</P>
<P>
