force Habibollah Sayyari said that the maneuvers with a code name
Me'raj (ascension) would be held around Qeshm island in the
Persian Gulf. According to the official news agency IRNA, Sayyari
did not mention the exact date of the maneuver but said that the
goal behind the maneuvers was to raise the naval forces' combat
readiness. (Iran-Maneuvers-Gulf) 
</P>
