<HEADLINE> Sichuan Improves Use Of Foreign Investment </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CHENGDU, September 17 (Xinhua) -- Southwest China's Sichuan
Province has achieved notable progress in the use of foreign
investment, with contracted investments for the first half of this
year hitting 357 million US dollars, up 36.6 percent on the 1997
period.
