against Vaughn Bean, the IBF's No. 1 challenger.
</P>
<P>
The fight is scheduled on Saturday night in the Georgia
Dome,Atlanta, and the arena is set up for 42,000 for the fight.
Holyfield is back home and his friends and neighbors seem happy
to see the heavyweight champion in their hometown.
</P>
